{"tid":203929,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拍「十二道雞子味」寸謝霆鋒勁吸like   失明廚神：你做到我哋都做到","createTime":"2017-04-16T15:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T17:00:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"138e49e2cba5e441c0fadaa54be603ed6968a415","tid":203929,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">拍「十二道雞子味」寸謝霆鋒勁吸like   失明廚神：你做到我哋都做到<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170415/56566481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170415%2F56566481&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=5dc5c58c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170415%2F56566481&h=7c204bee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170415/56566481</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170415/large/1492187624_b5bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170415%2Flarge%2F1492187624_b5bc.jpg&h=43916665&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n鄧光寶最近拍攝了一輯「十二道雞子味」串爆謝霆鋒，淋過毛巾的雞蛋仔、磨刀粉增鐵質，還有雞子撈丁黑暗料理，藝人扮型，他作灰諧。片段在網上播出兩日累積點擊近10萬，這名失明廚神笑說：「同佢玩吓啫」，但又確實有資格。5年前他已拍片教師奶買菜下廚，比姓謝的「出道」還早兩年。今次惡搞，也非純為抽水，「你謝霆鋒做到，我哋視障人士都做到」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wetv.hk/videos/1304837492903762/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwetv.hk%2Fvideos%2F1304837492903762%2F&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=c2981bfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wetv.hk/videos/1304837492903762/</a></span></div><br />\n<br />\n沒有影星老竇，也沒風流情史，鄧光寶只是一名「豬肉佬」，在街市打滾30年，由劏豬做到老闆，15年前卻患腦瘤一夜失明，結束生意，蝕賣層樓，宅在家2年，以為就此一生。但他天性樂觀，盲了雙眼，手腳健在，不想枉費半生經驗，5年前拍片放上網，教人買菜煮飯，沒多餘的矯揉造作，以貨真價實吸like，成本港首個殘疾人士網上電視台We Tv創台主持之一。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Wetv無障礙媒體<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wetv.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetv.hk%2F&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=b32d83ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wetv.hk/</a></span></div><br />\n<br />\n起初教煮家常便飯，木瓜魚尾湯、醉雞翼，近年鄧光寶鑽研失傳的懷舊美食，如野雞卷、金錢雞等，相當考功夫。口講無據，他即席炮製一碟豉椒排骨，鑊氣十足，切肉、起油、落鑊，全不假手於人。就如盧海一樣，雙目失明，也可自行組裝電腦，還開班教盲人用智能電話，更上網直播開講「盧Sir跟Phone教室」，教盲人用Apps改善生活。<br />\n<br />\n年逾60歲的盧Sir 20多年前視網膜逐漸退落，「我以為係假，有得醫」，由朦朧一片到眼前全黑，曾想過尋死，「覺得好絕望」。幸家人悉心照料，走過低谷，重新學走路、點字，還自學組裝電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、寫網站和手機應用程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。由昔日的餐廳老闆到今天當上IT人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，盧Sir相信互聯網能讓盲人與世界接軌，不用坐困愁城，「一般人做到，我哋都做到」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170414/large/1492181068_08f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170414%2Flarge%2F1492181068_08f7.jpg&h=d4204dfe&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n走過人生崎嶇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，總會多一份堅毅。志豪、光仔和阿鋒都因脊柱裂而下半身癱瘓，現時是輪椅籃球運動員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，正備戰挑戰賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。最近他們與隊友拍片講解輪椅籃球，如戰術、技巧等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，鼓勵更多殘疾人士參與，「好多殘疾人士覺得行唔到，手又唔夠力，搞咁多做乜，留喺屋企打機算啦」，志豪不認同，「越難做，更加要比心機去做」，比平常人更不言敗，「落得場就唔會放棄」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170414/large/1492181067_7d52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170414%2Flarge%2F1492181067_7d52.jpg&h=7a7c9859&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n失明人互聯會總幹事盛李廉表示，這班殘疾主持人今年更走出網台，落區到學校演講，鼓勵年輕人堅毅面對逆境，「佢哋好有鬥心，比到人真正嘅鼓勵」。"},{"pid":"bfdf008ea3e44401adc6e2282736ce5891d960c2","tid":203929,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"4ed84e9b8a622b59f4ef203305626949143b9857","tid":203929,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:59:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d73d74a821e6c6b43eace947fda6bf0ca9d4cca0","tid":203929,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"呢啲人真係好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}